      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "speaker_name": "阿罗逸多",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "老衲这人病怀绝症，欲求施主费心治疗，若动干戈胜你，施主勉强搭救甚为危险，老衲情愿送你一本武学秘本，内中所载绝非凡学，但望施主能救好这人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "text": "你怕我败后，便不尽力救他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "speaker_name": "阿罗逸多",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "老衲不愿动武，彼此不会有胜败。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "text": "但你要我救他，除非在武功上胜我，别无他法，莫说一本武学绝本，就是十本武学秘本我也不要！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "speaker_name": "阿罗逸多",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "一定要战？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "text": "别无他法！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "speaker_name": "阿罗逸多",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "那就战吧，老衲胜后，施主真要有把握一定将他治好？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "text": "你若不信，战有何用。抱他走吧！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "speaker_name": "红袍僧人",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "请施主发招。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "text": "出家人何方人氏？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "speaker_name": "阿罗逸多",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "老衲天竺阿罗逸多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "text": "他是何人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "speaker_name": "阿罗逸多",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "他是……他是……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "text": "他可是突厥人？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "speaker_name": "阿罗逸多",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "是……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
