      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "text": "你马上抱他离开，因他是突厥人氏，你纵然能胜我，我也不会救他！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "text": "对！突厥的狗子，救他做什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
