      "listener": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "text": "你快抱走，莫叫我见他一眼，否则别怪我史某动手杀害病人！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "史前辈，他们若再不走，在下帮你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "要你多嘴，还不快滚！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥，此人不知好歹，不要理他。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jue_bing_ren",
      "speaker_name": "突厥公子",
      "listener": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "text": "师父，他既不肯医治，徒儿一时无妨，只得再想他法。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "speaker_name": "阿罗逸多",
      "listener": "char_tu_jue_bing_ren",
      "text": "不行，你的怪病世上惟有他能救，今日无论如何，定要教他救治你？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_tu_jue_bing_ren",
      "text": "你没有死？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jue_bing_ren",
      "speaker_name": "突厥公子",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "姑娘说笑，在下若是死了，还会求医？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_tu_jue_bing_ren",
      "text": "可不一定，那位大爷有起死回生之术，你就是死了，他也可能把你救活，可惜你没死，就不能救啦！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jue_bing_ren",
      "speaker_name": "突厥公子",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "这话怎说？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_tu_jue_bing_ren",
      "text": "那位大爷现在只会救死人，不会救活人，你不妨死去一遍，看他就会救你。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "speaker_name": "阿罗逸多",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "别听那丫头乱嚼舌头，她在瞎说八道！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "史大爷，我可没有瞎说八道吧，待会他仍还不走，你将他们杀了，不是超度灵魂救了他们？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "野儿，别再胡说。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "speaker_name": "阿罗逸多",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "施主到底救不救？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "text": "你当真要史某超度你们师徒两人？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "speaker_name": "阿罗逸多",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "你有本领就将我杀了，没有本领教老衲擒住，不救也不成！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "text": "笑话，我会让你擒住。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "speaker_name": "阿罗逸多",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "不妨试试看！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "糟糕！史前辈恐怕不敌。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "史不旧一定不敌。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 285,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "你怎么知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "听师父说阿罗逸多是天竺一等高手，精通掌法，史不旧掌法平平，怎是对手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看红袍僧人如何能保不败？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "speaker_name": "阿罗逸多",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "注意啦！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "speaker_name": "阿罗逸多",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "着！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 313,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "speaker_name": "阿罗逸多",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "你找死！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "speaker_name": "阿罗逸多",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "看你还不就擒？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "speaker_name": "阿罗逸多",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "你还敢再战？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "text": "当然要战！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "浮天沧海远，去世泛舟轻……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 331,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "其中神妙奥秘，尽在此言中。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 349,
      "line_end": 351
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我了解了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 353,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "text": "怎么走啦？无妨再试试几拳！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 365,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "speaker_name": "阿罗逸多",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "总有一日老衲会将这路步法识破。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 369,
      "line_end": 369
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_a_luo_yi_duo",
      "text": "等你识破那日，怕已不在世上了！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 371,
      "line_end": 371
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "你能将师父教的那套步法练得这般熟悉，不错呀！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 375,
      "line_end": 377
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "当年令师为何只传走势，不传其中要诀？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 379,
      "line_end": 379
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "倘若那时家师要诀传你，今日世上还有何人能是你的敌手？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 381,
      "line_end": 383
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "令师难道怕老夫横行江湖，只传半套武功？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 385,
      "line_end": 387
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "就是家师的半套武功传你，还不知足！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 389,
      "line_end": 389
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "今日你为何将要诀说出？",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 391,
      "line_end": 391
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "你破例救我一命，我当然也要回报一次。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 393,
      "line_end": 393
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "寒……寒……毒……掌……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 395,
      "line_end": 395
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "寒毒掌？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 397,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "快……去……房中……取出……三……阳……丹……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 401,
      "line_end": 401
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "给……给……我！",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 405,
      "line_end": 405
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好厉害！好厉害！总算将那寒毒解了大半！",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 409,
      "line_end": 411
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "天下会寒毒掌的人有多少？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 411,
      "line_end": 413
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你们怎么还没走？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 415,
      "line_end": 417
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "你这人真不知好歹，我们若走早就走了，大哥没给你递药，现在早就冻死了，还能凶霸霸地说话！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 419,
      "line_end": 421
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "药是我的，那小子不过举手之劳而已！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 423,
      "line_end": 423
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "好没良心！好没良心……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 425,
      "line_end": 425
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "什么良心不良心，你师父根本没有回报我一次，一灯那贼尼本应该传我一套武功，她骗人只传半套，现在你将另半说出，等于替你师父消弥骗人的罪过……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 427,
      "line_end": 427
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "你敢骂我师父！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 429,
      "line_end": 429
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "但是老夫也未救你……",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 431,
      "line_end": 431
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "你没有救我，那我身上魔蓝毒是谁解去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 433,
      "line_end": 433
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "是他将你治好，我们走吧！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 435,
      "line_end": 435
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "你别走动，好好听着，你的性命是换来的……",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 437,
      "line_end": 437
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "你敢说！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 439,
      "line_end": 439
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "现在老夫将凌波微步体会透彻，不会再输给你了！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 441,
      "line_end": 443
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "你说，我的性命是怎样换来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 445,
      "line_end": 445
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "叫你别动，可没错吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 449,
      "line_end": 449
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "她怎么啦？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 451,
      "line_end": 451
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你管她怎么啦，她虽不能自由走动，总比你只能活两年好得多。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 453,
      "line_end": 455
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥，是你用性命换我的性命－－",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 459,
      "line_end": 459
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "莫听他胡说，你怎么不能走动？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 461,
      "line_end": 461
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你问她有什么用，她也不知道。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 463,
      "line_end": 463
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "前辈是否将她治好了？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 465,
      "line_end": 465
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我也没法治，魔蓝毒解得太迟，这双脚今生莫想再走动自如。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 467,
      "line_end": 469
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "我不信世上没有药能将野儿的腿伤治好！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 471,
      "line_end": 471
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "有是有的，但凭你怎能要到那药物？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 473,
      "line_end": 473
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "什么药物？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 475,
      "line_end": 475
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我没有义务要告诉你！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 477,
      "line_end": 477
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "你说不说？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 479,
      "line_end": 479
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "他不说罢了，你既只能活两年，我腿好了有什么用！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 481,
      "line_end": 483
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "他胡说，我再活几十年也没问题，你的腿伤一定要治好，他若不治，誓不罢休！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 485,
      "line_end": 487
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你骗她有什么用，老夫那颗药丸巨毒无比，两年后一定发作，即使华陀再世，到时也没法救你一命。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 489,
      "line_end": 491
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥可是为了救我，将他那颗毒药丸吃下？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 493,
      "line_end": 493
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "没这回事，是他败在我的剑下，不得不救你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 495,
      "line_end": 497
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "你敢否认不是败在我的剑下，不得不治？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 497,
      "line_end": 499
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不错！但……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 501,
      "line_end": 501
    }
  ],
